Package: exams.wuvienna
Title: Question Generation in the MyLearn XML Format
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Darjus",
           family = "Hosszejni",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "darjus.hosszejni@wu.ac.at",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3803-691X"))
Description: Randomized multiple-select and single-select
  question generation for the MyLearn platform at the Vienna
  University of Economics and Business. Question templates
  in the form of the R/exams package (see <http://www.r-exams.org/>)
  are transformed into MyLearn's XML format.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
  exams (>= 2.3-4),
  glue (>= 1.4.0),
  stringr (>= 1.4.0),
  xml2 (>= 1.2.5)
URL: https://learn.wu.ac.at
BugReports: https://github.com/hdarjus/WU-MyLearn-QGen/issues
